{"tid":2169421,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊大台劇]有冇人記得當年火舞黃沙有首消失咗既插曲?","createTime":"2020-08-22T13:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T09:23:32.000Z","uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"455a5190b430c6c12f1dbaee8b29530e0b41cad8","tid":2169421,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:07:50.000Z","msg":"仲記得當年火舞黃沙播個陣,有好多人屌9林保怡唱個首主題曲難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早排無聊睇返,發現原來套劇入面有首消失咗既插曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首插曲之所以叫消失咗,係因為wiki入面都冇記載<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%81%AB%E8%88%9E%E9%BB%83%E6%B2%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%2588%259E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B2%2599&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=e4c55fcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%81%AB%E8%88%9E%E9%BB%83%E6%B2%99</a><br />\n用google大神幫手,搵到首歌叫最好的時光<br />\n唱個位歌手叫蔡瑋瑜,google過應該係業餘歌手,幫大台唱過幾首插曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/HK-drama/M.1414551769.A.0F0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FHK-drama%2FM.1414551769.A.0F0.html&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=bd371e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/HK-drama/M.1414551769.A.0F0.html</a><br />\n香港應該冇咩人記得呢首歌,但台灣PPT竟然有人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上首歌係youtube,支那D影片網都搵唔到<br />\n唯有係套劇某D片段用來做BGM<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV14W41197NB/?spm_id_from=333.788.videocard.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2FBV14W41197NB%2F%3Fspm_id_from%3D333.788.videocard.1&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=28dc0d77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV14W41197NB/?spm_id_from=333.788.videocard.1</a><br />\n(原諒個貼支那野,但呢D片段因版權問題只有係B站搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n3:34分左右開始段BGM就係首歌<br />\n<br />\n有冇人記得呢首消失咗既插曲?想搵返來聽可以有咩途徑?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c92136ed8f6c64e1358d832836e9389775844d","tid":2169421,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"個阿姑喺狗面前拎刀隊人都有得保釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2169225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2169225</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"488a9f5758bfa8ef9c4dd46d86d416c8e0607789","tid":2169421,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248991364da5d8c8f897ebc0334d1c28b91fa0dc","tid":2169421,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}